WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:06.900
In Italy, before getting married,

2
00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:08.060
it's usually necessary to make

3
00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:09.400
a marriage announcement at the city hall.

4
00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:11.340
It usually takes about two weeks to announce the marriage,

5
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:13.180
to ensure there are no objections

6
00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:14.540
or other legal issues.

7
00:00:15.240 --> 00:00:17.460
If someone objects during the announcement period,

8
00:00:17.820 --> 00:00:19.700
will the marriage not be valid?

9
00:00:32.630 --> 00:00:34.550
What's the act?

10
00:00:35.690 --> 00:00:38.090
Jin Lingling, I originally planned to let you go to that

11
00:00:38.090 --> 00:00:41.530
substandard school. Since you've fallen asleep,

12
00:00:41.690 --> 00:00:44.370
then...

13
00:00:44.370 --> 00:00:46.510
I...

14
00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:51.220
Huo Jiuling? How did you get back?

15
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:52.820
What did you just say?

16
00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:53.760
Sunset.

17
00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.100
What's with the acting?

18
00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.140
Ah? I don't understand.

19
00:01:00.580 --> 00:01:02.600
Nothing. Since you're sleepy,

20
00:01:02.940 --> 00:01:03.760
just go to sleep.

21
00:01:05.780 --> 00:01:07.180
You're going to sleep here tonight?

22
00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.420
Where else would I sleep, Mrs. Huo?

